*&quot;Conifers of California&quot; (1999), by Ronald M. Lanner, .
*&quot;Wildflowers of the Sierra Nevada and the Central Valley&quot; (1998), by Laird R. Blackwell, .
*&quot;Sierra Nevada Wildflowers&quot; (1998), by Elizabeth L. Horn, .
*&quot;California Forests and Woodlands: A Natural History&quot; (1996), by Verna R. Johnston, Carla J. Simmons (Illustrator), .
*&quot;A Sierra Nevada Flora&quot; (1996), by Norman L Weeden and Amy David, .
*&quot;Manual of California Vegetation&quot; (1995), by Todd Keeler-Wolf and John Sawyer, .
*&quot;The Jepson Manual: Higher Plants of California &quot; (1993) by James C Hickman, .
*&quot;Oaks of California&quot; (1990), by Bruce M. Pavlik, Sharon Johnson, Pamela Muick, Marjorie Popper, .
*&quot;Lingering in Tahoe&#x27;s Wild Gardens: A Guide to Hundreds of the Most Beautiful Wildflower Gardens of the Tahoe Region&quot; (1989), by Julie Carville, .
