<text>Reuter or Reutter is a surname. Notable people with the surname include:

==Reuter==
* Christian Reuter (1665– 1712), writer
* Edzard Reuter (1928–2024), Daimler-Benz manager
* Émile Reuter (1874–1973), Luxembourgian politician
