<doc id="1158116" wikidata="Q3837500" url="?curid=1158116" title="Wrestling at the 2004 Summer Olympics – Men's Greco-Roman 96 kg">
<text>The men&#x27;s Greco-Roman 96 kilograms at the [[2004 Summer Olympics]] as part of the wrestling program were held at the Ano Liosia Olympic Hall, August 25 to August 26.

The competition held with an elimination system of three or four wrestlers in each pool, with the winners qualify for the quarterfinals, semifinals and final by way of direct elimination.

